-list:l1 level1 lfo2;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >（1）<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >集团竞聘</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:28.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >根据集团要求，对管理岗位人员实行集团竞聘制度，按照集团要求上报竞聘岗位信息，由集团实施相关招聘程序。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=15  style="margin-left:72.0000pt;text-indent:-36.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo2;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >（2）<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >校园招聘</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:28.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >通过</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >加强</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >校企合作，</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >打造</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >雇主品牌，</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >强化</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >校园招聘。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >与高校签订生产学研实践基地合作协议，为大四的本科生提供为期</font>6<font face="宋体" >天的生产实践学习，为大三学生提供学习参观；与高职院校签订校企合作的协议，为学生提供实习的机会；作为</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >嘉宾参加高校的</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >职业</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >生涯</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >规划</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >课程和就业辅导课程，</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >以此树立公司良好的企业雇主品牌形象。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:28.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >通过在各大高校就业网站上发布招聘信息，组织</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >校园宣讲会、</font></span><span style=